PSY feuding with artist tenants of his Seoul building FILE - In this June 18, 2014 file photo, South Korean rapper PSY, center, performs with dancers before a TV broadcasting 2014 Brazil World Cup Group H game between South Korea and Russia at a public viewing venue in Seoul, South Korea. PSY is fighting an ugly legal battle with artist tenants who are reluctant to leave a building he owns in Seoul. Choi Jee Ahn of Takeout Drawing said Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015 that about 10 lawsuits have been exchanged between a gallery the artists belong to and their YouTube star landlord.
